						<div class="current-issue__content-article js-open-overlayer" data-href="/journal/143/590415/counterinsurgent-cop-city-abolition-ecology-and-the-aesthetics-of-counterreform/">
							<a href="/journal/143/590415/counterinsurgent-cop-city-abolition-ecology-and-the-aesthetics-of-counterreform/">
								<span class="current-issue__content-article-title">
									Counterinsurgent: Cop City, Abolition Ecology, and the Aesthetics of Counterreform
								</span>

								<span class="current-issue__content-article-author">
									T. J. Demos
								</span>
